content: Without a doubt, this is one of the most visually pleasing flight simulators out there. The aircraft are a great experience to fly with fully functioning flightdecks. Clouds and visuals like sun glares make up for a perfect flying experience. From a flight perspective, the flight models have slight issues (roll speeds on airliners are quite fast, stalls are not simulated very well, and some other minor issues). In conclusion, it is a great simulator to explore the skies and is well developed.

I will say, however, it is nice being able to pay one price and get all the aircraft for free!
